<expan>ἐμπόρου<ex>ς</ex></expan>·

    <lb n="13"/>τὰ δʼ ἄ<supplied reason="omitted">λ</supplied>λα
σεα<supplied reason="omitted">υ</supplied>τοῦ ἐπιμέλου ἵνʼ ὑγ<surplus>ε</surplus>ιαίνησ<surplus><unclear>ς</unclear></surplus>.

    <lb n="14"/>#331 #331

